"37:165:3" : {s: 37, a: 165, w: 3, r: "صفف", t: "ٱلصَّآفُّونَ", l: "صَّآفُّون", lc: 1, tl: "l-ṣāfūna", lb: "কাতারবদ্ধ, সারিবদ্ধ",e: "stand in rows", b: "সারিবদ্ধ", i: "bersaf-saf", f: 1, rm: "evenly, side by side, laid out, a rank/row/line, in order, with reference to a bird: extend its wings in a line, expand/spread its wings (i.e. not flapping)."},
