"37:167:2" : {s: 37, a: 167, w: 2, r: "كون", t: "كَانُوا۟", l: "كَانَ", lc: 1358, tl: "kānū", lb: "হয়, হতো",e: "they used to", b: "তারা করত/হতো/ছিল", i: "mereka adalah", f: 229, rm: "To be, exist, happen, occur, take place, become, be such or so, originated."},
"37:167:3" : {s: 37, a: 167, w: 3, r: "قول", t: "لَيَقُولُونَ", l: "قَالَ", lc: 1618, tl: "layaqūlūna", lb: "কথা বলা",e: "say", b: "অবশ্যই তারা বলে", i: "pasti mereka akan berkata", f: 4, rm: "to say/speak, to call, to be named, word/speech, utterance, a thing said, greeting, discourse, one who says/speaks. To inspire/transmit/relate/answer/think/profess, emit an opinion on, indicate a state or condition or circumstance. qailun - speaker, indicator."},
